{"tid":1377265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"善用1823","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:26:23.000Z","uid":119144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f576c7d1cbacafabc2ccae2d2765634046cc33","tid":1377265,"uid":119144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得1823係一個好好嘅途徑。<br />\n我覺得政府真係好愛我地，比呢個途徑我地表達意見。<br />\n為左令政府各部門，清楚了解到每區嘅問題。<br />\n我希望各位，為左令好愛我地嘅政府對我地唔好失望，記住 記住 記住 要將你地區嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有</span></span>問題，例如 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">交通問題</span></span> ，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">治安問題</span></span>，如實<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">經常</span></span>反映。<br />\n記住記低案件編號，以便作出跟進。<br />\n每個部門收到1823就必須要處理。<br />\n如果唔處理，唔知可唔可以寄信比好打得嘅特首辦呢？<br />\n利申：用左兩次，發現香港公務員好盡責。<br />\n香港加油！兄弟爬山！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}